<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Northern Red Oak</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f7fb;
      color: #12233d;
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .card {
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      border-top: 8px solid #f58220;
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      color: #002855;
    }
    .latin {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      color: #5e6f8c;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .row {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .label {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #002855;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      background: #f58220;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>Northern Red Oak</h1>
    <p class="latin">Quercus rubra</p>

    <div class="row"><span class="label">Tree ID:</span> T001</div>
    <div class="row"><span class="label">Planting Year:</span> 1998</div>
    <div class="row"><span class="label">DBH:</span> 48 cm</div>
    <div class="row"><span class="label">Health:</span> Good</div>
    <div class="row"><span class="label">Location:</span> Library Walk</div>

    <p>
      Large shade tree with a broad canopy. Healthy structure and strong seasonal color.
    </p>

    <a class="btn" href="https://maps.google.com/?q=42.5033,-70.8890" target="_blank">
      View Location
    </a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
